@UserManagementAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5066
@AuthToken = Bearer mi-token-valido

### Obtener todos los usuarios
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{AuthToken}}

###

### Obtener un usuario específico por ID (ej. ID 1)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{AuthToken}}

###

### Crear un nuevo usuario
POST {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{AuthToken}}

{
  "name": "Carlos Gomez",
  "email": "carlos@example.com",
  "department": "Ventas"
}

###

### Actualizar un usuario existente (ej. actualizar a Alice, ID 1)
PUT {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{AuthToken}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Alice Smith Modificada",
  "email": "alice.nueva@example.com",
  "department": "Legal"
}

###

### Eliminar un usuario (ej. eliminar a Bob, ID 2)
DELETE {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/users/2
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{AuthToken}}

###
